---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 427
  - Title: The Sophic Hydrolith
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=Deviation
---
If you in any way abuse the gift of God, or use it for your own
glorification, you will most certainly be called to account by the
Almighty Giver, and you will think that it would have been better for
you if you had never known it.
